# Finance Advisor AI

A personal finance advisory system combining Machine Learning and Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG). Users input their financial data and receive ML-based profiling plus personalized advice generated by Claude AI.

## Architecture

```
User Input (FastAPI)
       ↓
ML Pipeline (GMM + Random Forest)
       ↓                    ↓
User Segment          Cash Flow Status
       ↓                    ↓
       └──── RAG Engine (ChromaDB + sentence-transformers) ────┘
                            ↓
                  Claude API (claude-sonnet-4-6)
                            ↓
              Personalized Financial Advice
```

## Tech Stack

- **ML Models**: Scikit-learn (GMM Clustering, Random Forest Classifier)
- **RAG**: sentence-transformers (`all-MiniLM-L6-v2`), ChromaDB
- **LLM**: Anthropic Claude API (`claude-sonnet-4-6`)
- **Backend**: FastAPI + Uvicorn
- **Data**: Personal Finance Tracker dataset (3,000 records, 25 features)

